{"id":1729594,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-11T12:12:51.765Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1729594,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Pekan Kecil Kampung Terpencil","overview":"# The Story  The story begins in a remote village whose community lives in harmony like one big family. Regardless of their race, they all help and respect one another. On the day they receive the arrival of a dome for their small mosque (collected from all the villagers), they also receive the arrival of a woman, Dara, who previously worked there. All the villagers' attention is directed towards a young man named Wadud, whom they all know had once been in love with that woman. The epic love story between the two of them now becomes the talk of the entire village. From the young to the old, each tells about this epic love story. However, they still cannot find the answer to why Wadud and Dara separated. Seeds of conflict begin to emerge among the villagers as each one maintains their own answer about the separation of this epic love affair. The village chief begins to realize the situation among the villagers. An emergency meeting is held to resolve the issue.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/qrvxpku14Hfopf5aN20wvRv0xLo.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":119729,"logo_path":null,"name":"Unit Drama TV RTM","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2022-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Pekan Kecil Kampung Terpencil","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2463008,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Che Kem","original_name":"Che Kem","popularity":0.0286,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a51647418b883649f205d6c","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1